'''Servo'''是一個由[[Mozilla基金會|Mozilla]]開發的實驗性[[網頁瀏覽器|網頁瀏覽器]][[排版引擎|排版引擎]]，[[三星集團|三星集團]]移植到[[Android|Android]]系统和[[ARM|ARM]]处理器<ref>{{cite news |url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/04/samsung-teams-up-with-mozilla-to-build-browser-engine-for-multicore-machines/ |title=Samsung teams up with Mozilla to build browser engine for multicore machines |publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |date=2013-04-03 |accessdate=2014-10-24 |archive-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216003838/http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/04/samsung-teams-up-with-mozilla-to-build-browser-engine-for-multicore-machines/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該项目旨在创造一个大規模[[平行計算|平行計算]]的环境，其中许多组件（如[[渲染|算繪]]、布局、HTML解析、图像[[解码|解码]]等）都是[[任務並行|並行]]的。此项目与[[Rust|Rust]]编程语言有共生的关系，并同样正在开发中。

Servo使用的两个重要组件基于Mozilla现有的[[C++|C++]]代码。[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]支持由[[SpiderMonkey|SpiderMonkey]]提供，2D图形库{{le|Mozilla Azure|Mozilla Azure|Azure}}用于与[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]和[[Direct3D|Direct3D]]交互。<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://lwn.net/Articles/647969/ |title= Parallel page rendering with Mozilla Servo |publisher= [[LWN.net|LWN.net]] |last1= Willis |first1= Nathan |date= 17 June 2015 |accessdate= 27 June 2015 |archive-date= 2016-04-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160406021924/https://lwn.net/Articles/647969/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

Servo是以美國影集《神秘科學戲院3000》（{{lang|en|''Mystery Science Theater 3000''}}）的機器人Tom Servo命名的<ref>{{cite web|last=Eich|first=Brendan|title=Add a new UI crate|url=https://github.com/mozilla/servo/issues/111#issuecomment-9415000|accessdate=2014-04-02}}</ref>。

== 發展 ==
[[File:Mozilla_Research_projects.png|thumb]]

Servo發展尚處於起步階段，然而，它已經可以算繪[[維基百科|維基百科]]和[[GitHub|GitHub]]，並成功通過了[[Acid2|Acid2]]測試。它具有諸如並行排版演算法以及在Rust中實現的自己的CSS3和HTML5解析器<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://blog.mozilla.org/research/2014/04/17/another-big-milestone-for-servo-acid2/ |last= Moffitt |first= Jack |date= April 17, 2014 |title= Another Big Milestone for Servo—Acid2 |accessdate= 2015-11-26 |archive-date= 2016-05-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160517141825/https://blog.mozilla.org/research/2014/04/17/another-big-milestone-for-servo-acid2/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= https://blog.servo.org/2015/05/01/forward/ |date= May 1, 2015 |title= Servo Continues Pushing Forward |accessdate= 2015-11-26 |archive-date= 2016-04-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160407203205/http://blog.servo.org/2015/05/01/forward/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。Servo利用[[GPU|GPU]]加速技術更快速和流暢地呈現網頁<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bergstrom|first1=Lars|title=Mozilla's Project Quantum and Servo|url=https://groups.google.com/forum/m/#!topic/mozilla.dev.servo/3bH1KaqJq0s|website=mozilla.dev.servo - Google Groups|accessdate=9 November 2016|archive-date=2019-03-14|archive-url=https://archive.today/20190314091543/https://groups.google.com/forum/m/%23!topic/soc.culture.tamil/BCnIDKAkH6Y/discussion#!topic/mozilla.dev.servo/3bH1KaqJq0s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Clark|first1=Lin|title=The whole web at maximum FPS: How WebRender gets rid of jank|url=https://hacks.mozilla.org/2017/10/the-whole-web-at-maximum-fps-how-webrender-gets-rid-of-jank/|website=Mozilla Hacks – the Web developer blog|accessdate=22 October 2017|date=10 October 2017|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104175920/https://hacks.mozilla.org/2017/10/the-whole-web-at-maximum-fps-how-webrender-gets-rid-of-jank/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Servo發展始於2012年。2012年2月8日第一次提交沒有包含任何[[原始碼|原始碼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/servo/servo/commit/ce30d4520d67f2c6ef960571a9b3e450c5dcbebe|title=initial add · servo/servo@ce30d45|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2019-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217220110/https://github.com/servo/servo/commit/ce30d4520d67f2c6ef960571a9b3e450c5dcbebe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年3月27日第一個基本代碼提交<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/servo/servo/commit/783455f684bc613dba25d5c2e54157c336093f35|title=Add some stubs and a makefile · servo/servo@783455f|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2019-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217220110/https://github.com/servo/servo/commit/783455f684bc613dba25d5c2e54157c336093f35|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年4月3日，Mozilla宣布和三星合作開發Servo<ref>{{cite web|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2013/04/03/mozilla-and-samsung-collaborate-on-next-generation-web-browser-engine/|title=Mozilla and Samsung Collaborate on Next Generation Web Browser Engine|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023082731/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2013/04/03/mozilla-and-samsung-collaborate-on-next-generation-web-browser-engine/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidcentral.com/mozilla-samsung-team-servo-next-gen-browser-engine|title=Mozilla, Samsung team up on 'Servo' next-gen browser engine|publisher=|access-date=2017-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109191451/https://www.androidcentral.com/mozilla-samsung-team-servo-next-gen-browser-engine|archive-date=2017-11-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2014年11月，Servo在某些基準測試中的速度明顯快於[[Gecko|Gecko]]和其他排版引擎<ref>{{cite web|last1=Larabel|first1=Michael|title=Mozilla's Servo Engine Is Crazy Fast Compared To Gecko|url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTgzNDA|website=Phoronix|accessdate=10 May 2016|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024202601/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTgzNDA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mozilla's Servo Is Whooping The Other Browsers In Performance|url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Google-Servo-Perf-Comparison|website=Phoronix|accessdate=10 May 2016|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930132457/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Google-Servo-Perf-Comparison|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年6月30日，Mac和Linux的預覽版可供下載<ref>{{cite web|title=Servo Nightly Builds Available|url=http://blog.servo.org/2016/06/30/servo-nightlies/|website=Servo Blog|date=30 June 2016|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2017-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011233726/https://blog.servo.org/2016/06/30/servo-nightlies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年4月13日，構建版可用於Windows<ref>{{cite web|title=Windows nightly builds now available|url=https://blog.servo.org/2017/04/13/windows/|website=Servo Blog|date=13 April 2017|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226152729/https://blog.servo.org/2017/04/13/windows/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，隨著Firefox 54的發布，Mozilla將Servo CSS樣式引擎整合到了其Gecko瀏覽器引擎<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Servo engines written in Rust deliver memory safety and multithreading|url=https://research.mozilla.org/servo-engines|access-date=2020-07-05|website=Mozilla Research|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112102601/https://research.mozilla.org/servo-engines/}}</ref>。 

2020年8月，受到[[嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎疫情|嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎疫情]]影響，由於缺乏資金和組織重組，Mozilla裁撤了大部分Servo開發團隊<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/mozilla-lays-off-250-employees-while-it-refocuses-on-commercial-products/ |title=Mozilla lays off 250 employees while it refocuses on commercial products |date=2020-08-11 |access-date=2020-08-17 |archive-date=2022-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318025804/https://www.zdnet.com/article/mozilla-lays-off-250-employees-while-it-refocuses-on-commercial-products/ }}</ref>。2020年11月17日起，Servo由[[Linux基金會|Linux基金會]]接管<ref>{{Cite web|title=Servo’s new home|url=https://blog.servo.org/2020/11/17/servo-home/|date=2020-11-17|work=blog.servo.org|access-date=2021-03-16|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520000447/https://blog.servo.org/2020/11/17/servo-home/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Servo 成为 Linux 基金会托管项目|editor=WinterIsComing|date=2020-11-18|website=[[Solidot|Solidot]]|url=https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=66121|accessdate=2021-01-10|archive-date=2022-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426003503/https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=66121}}</ref>。

